## R Markdown

I follow this link: <https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/rtweet/vignettes/auth.html> 

```{r }
## load rtweet
library(rtweet)

## store api keys (these are fake example values; replace with your own keys)
api_key <- "SH1jq3B3kHTCKdBVtX4eTJyQ8"
api_secret_key <- "yHCaHNmHqHWvAIgVX3vufX8T7aB4vNbVb4Rpi2hDtfLeRaojHm"

## authenticate via web browser
token <- create_token(
  app = "rstatsjournalismresearch",
  consumer_key = api_key,
  consumer_secret = api_secret_key)
```

